@startuml 19-ask-streaming
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Ask Mode (Streaming Answer)

actor User
participant "AskModePage" as UI
participant "Rate limiter" as RL
participant "POST /api/ask" as API
participant "IEmbeddingClient" as EC
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "pgvector" as DB
participant "PromptBuilder" as PB
participant "IChatClient" as CC
participant "LLM provider" as P

User -> UI: type question, send
UI -> RL: POST /api/ask (SSE)
RL -> RL: per-user 20/min
alt under limit
    RL -> API: forward
    API -> EC: EmbedAsync(q)
    EC --> API: qv
    API -> CTX: SqlQuery top-8 hits
    CTX -> DB: CTE search
    DB --> CTX: rows
    API -> PB: System(hits)
    PB --> API: system prompt
    API -> CC: StreamAsync(system, question)
    CC -> P: chat.completions.stream
    loop tokens
        P --> CC: token
        CC --> API: token
        API --> UI: event: token\ndata: "..."
        UI -> UI: append to answer bubble
    end
    P --> CC: [DONE]
    CC --> API: end
    API --> UI: event: done
    UI --> User: full answer shown
else over limit
    RL --> UI: 429 Retry-After
    UI --> User: "Too many questions, try again"
end

@enduml
